{"title":"千里炉火映天烧——雪夜怀炼钢","authors":["海棱"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":12,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里炉火映天烧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——雪夜怀炼钢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海棱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满眼风光瑞雪飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里炉火映天烧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南北东西人如海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮日涨万丈高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮日涨万丈高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金龙飞舞绝代骄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾空万马势如雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叱咤风云大地摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叱咤风云大地摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗在手缚苍蛟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河山换色越千载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族同心颂舜尧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族同心颂舜尧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄辈出数今朝；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能阻挡东流水？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且看长江浪滔滔。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}